VERO BEACH’S BEST KEPT SECRET!
Midway Estates is an active adult community that has 104 home sites and 73 RV sites!
Midway Estates is located in beautiful Vero Beach, FL.  As one of the state’s most popular destinations, Vero Beach is primarily known for its breathtaking beaches, and wide variety of natural, cultural, recreational activities and its inviting climate makes playing golf and sport fishing a joy throughout the year.
Midway Estates is home to friendly, caring and fun-loving residents.
Whether you’re looking to relax or get active, Midway Estates is ready to serve you!
